textAfterTable: Property Description A remodeled 3 story beach house for your family with room to spare.  Breath taking sunsets on the rooftop terrace of this remodeled house. Over 2500 sq feet with two living areas and TVs in almost every room including the master bath. Wake up and sit on the balcony with your morning coffee and look at the beauty of Clearwater Beach.  Then walk a few steps to the powdery, white sands for a day of sun and swimming.  Mid-day come back home for a Bar-b-que and lunch on your private patio and the relax with some pool time.  No large condo complex to walk thru. Park at your front door. Just easy access to the beach.  Then search for your favorite restaurant within walking distance - Frenchy''s, Tates, ClearwaterSkye, Calis, Carettas and more.
